   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1899_AS_RBH_3_00049"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Rich.
                     Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb190427" type="place">I. Wollzeile 15</rs></hi>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1899_AS_RBH_3_00048"/><salute>lieber Richard,</salute> bitte kommen Sie in die <rs type="place" ref="#pmb14" subtype="implied"><rs type="event" ref="#pmb43208" subtype="implied"><rs type="work" ref="#pmb30827 #pmb30403 #pmb29845"><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01006-1"/>Loge 6<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01006-1">Das <rs type="org" ref="#pmb36247">Burgtheater</rs>
                        veranstaltete eine gemeinsame <rs type="event" ref="#pmb43208" subtype="implied">Aufführung von <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzlers</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="work" ref="#pmb30403">Paracelus</rs> und <rs type="work" ref="#pmb29845">Die Gefährtin</rs>
                        mit dem Dramenfragment <rs type="work" ref="#pmb30827">Esther</rs> von <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11518">Franz Grillparzer</rs></rs>,
                        <ref type="schnitzler-kultur" target="pmb43208" subtype="cf"/>.
                     </note></rs></rs></rs>, rechts, 1. Gallerie!</p><p>Ich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>elb<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t bin bei <rs ref="#pmb12671" type="person">Schlenther</rs>. Nachtmahlen
                  ka<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> ich nicht mit Ihnen; <rs ref="#pmb2461" type="person" subtype="implied"><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chwe<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>terlicher</rs> Geburtstag.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr<lb/><signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
